<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="29Oct1940"><font color="red">29 October 1940</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Gustav Zumsteg): The Legation of the U.S.A. at Berne writes me that when I reach Switzerland I can receive my money from New York &hellip; As for the financial guarantee, since Mr R. Brauchbar has not given it (at least up to 27 October) my friends the Giedions have given it. </div>
